,"uid":20302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T09:17:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>愛唔係大哂  <br />\n<br />\n好多野唔夾都會間接磨蝕你地既熱情同愛</blockquote><br />\n我地好果陣真係好好 咩都好夾 只係一嗌起交就好大鑊 有時會嚴重到講分手 但係兩個都知係唔會分手 只係想要人氹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初初我同ex 都好夾 好明白大家 又唔會點樣爭執 <br />\n<br />\n但耐左之後好多野要面對  壓力一大  處理手法大家都唔同 出現左好多分歧  慢慢就破壞左我地關係 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd4b458a7566be0eb47f33805845a70dc4b470d5","tid":197581,"uid":76884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Same<br />\n感覺依家係延遲死期，唉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係你問題係對方有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但大家都好愛對方<br />\n<br />\n成日噪真係好辛苦</blockquote><br />\n一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鬧交鬧到好攰 但係真係唔想分手</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n啱啱先鬧左獲勁既<br />\n琴日又有<br />\n好似日日都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你地一齊左幾耐？<br />\n我地三年，前兩年相處好好<br />\n唔知係唔係佢開始做野有工作壓力令好多問題浮面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一齊咗年幾啦 好果陣係真係好開心 但係一鬧交就好似兩個人咁 我地呢排都成日嘈交 搞到關係好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e9ca65a7450af047ecd817e2bf2e426e6b0582","tid":197581,"uid":102190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T10:36:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>走。唔係自己杯茶會好難飲，到最後只會傷害自己。<br />\n利申：拍左6年半，對方咩問題都衰過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 近排忍唔住分左手</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講下因為d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n性格差，脾氣唔好，相處期間唔開心多過開心，我成日單向為佢付出，搞到好大壓力。<br />\n拍拖拍到唔開心就放棄啦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我經歷緊喎<br />\n我深信緊付出過後會有成果<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當你一直付出，然後又一直失望，一而再再而三，你會好想放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你有冇同佢反映過先？不過有時反映完之後會好矛盾，你會覺得你對佢反映好似強逼佢咁，到改咗之後又好似變嗮質，冇咗一開始鍾意佢個種感覺，最未都係頂唔順，分手"},{"pid":"66a18e3ab7d5234967c1c77fee187b31e60bfbb9","tid":197581,"uid":99362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:21:01.000Z","msg":"我同我男朋友拍拖拍左就尼三年<br />\n我仲係好愛佢 但佢就成日都唔覆我whapsapp<br />\n又唔揾我 有時直頭係兩個星期先見一次<br />\n好似真係唔洗揾唔洗見禁<br />\n就連叫佢係ig到po我地既合照都唔肯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係唔知佢發生咩事情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n問佢係咪想分手 佢又話唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真係唔知佢想點 Diu"}]}